## Updated Protocols

This folder contains experimental protocols that have been updated and refined since our previous publication.

The procedures are based on the methods described in:
Ribeiro, R.P., Null, R.W., Ã–zpolat, D.B. (2025) Sex-biased gene expression precedes sexual dimorphism in the agonadal annelid Platynereis dumerilii. Development, 152 (7): dev204513. https://doi.org/10.1242/dev.204513 

Updates include clarifications, optimizations, and minor modifications introduced during subsequent experiments. These changes do not alter the conceptual framework of the original methods but improve reproducibility and usability.

